      "parameters": {
        "content": "## S4 \u00b7 01 \u00b7 HTTP Methods Tour\n\nOne node per HTTP verb against your FastAPI playground.\nSee verbs as **intent**, not syntax:\n- **GET** = read\n- **POST** = create\n- **PUT** = replace\n- **PATCH** = update part\n- **DELETE** = remove\n\nPUT/PATCH/DELETE hit endpoints that don't exist in main.py \u2014 you'll see **405 Method Not Allowed**. That's the lesson.",
